&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a full time Locum Consultant who will provide clinical leadership for the South East Locality Team based at St Ann&#39;s Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The South East Locality Team is a designated trial team for the ODESSI trial – a landmark randomised controlled multicentre study into the feasibility of Open Dialogue in an NHS setting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A CQC inspection in 2019 rated the Trust as &#39;&#39;good&#39;&#39; for the first time, reflecting the dynamism and drive of the developments of the past few years. Colleagues joining the Trust at this point will have opportunity to contribute and shape the service during an exciting period of change and consolidation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is fixed term for a period of 6 months pending Royal College approval to recruit substantively. The post holder will be encouraged to apply for the substantive post following the locum period.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;*Strictly no agencies please&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr Katrin Edelman, Clinical Director for Haringey Services&lt;/p&gt;
